I will succeed in an imperial-examination,
become an official and save the world.

4
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,320
Great aspirations.

5
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,280
But

6
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:30,840
there is no conflict between
being an official and a princess's husband.

7
00:00:32,480 --> 00:00:33,720
Don't try to fool me, Princess.

8
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,210
Donglan's ancestral rule forbids

9
00:00:35,230 --> 00:00:36,970
the husbands of the royal family
from participating in politics.

10
00:00:38,320 --> 00:00:41,040
The rules can be bent a little bit.

11
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:42,080
Just like back in the day,

12
