Forget about it.

17
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:54,800
Never mind.

18
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,920
We still have a lot of time.

19
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:58,320
Let's solve the problem at hand.

20
00:00:58,440 --> 00:00:59,240
Mammy,

21
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:05,880
tell the kitchen to get ready.

22
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,080
He's going to take a cooking lesson.

23
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,360
Yes.

24
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,240
Princess.

25
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,840
When will you be done torturing me?

26
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,960
When you're willing

27
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,840
and capable of being my husband.

28
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:29,040
Cang Xiaoqi, without his memories,

29
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:30,320
can be a real pain in the ass.

30
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:34,120
He is a real pain in the ass.

31
00:01:36,320 --> 00:01:38,600
Why do you always show up out of nowhere?

32
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,640
You scared me.

33
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:41,120
Luckily I have a strong heart.

34
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,760
I'm so cute,

35
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,440
how can I scare anyone?

36
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,560
You are so young

37
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,720
and yet so self-obsessed.

38
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,880
I got that from my parents.

39
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,680
You know what,

40
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,720
you do look familiar to me.

41
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,200
I think I've seen you somewhere before.

42
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,480
The pot is about to explode.

43
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,000
What, pot?

44
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,200
What happened?

45
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,520
The pot exploded.

46
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:15,280
How did the pot explode?

47
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,920
There's oil in the pot
and the oil was boiling.

48
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,320
I said: Don't pour any water in it,

49
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,920
- but...
- But he said it too late.

50
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,120
So the pot exploded.

51
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,760
Luckily,

52
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,840
